        <p>
         <strong>
          SAB Staff Scholarship Award Program
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
         The UCSC Staff Advisory Board is pleased to announce our new Staff Scholarship Award Program. We hope to award our first scholarships soon for the career enhancement and professional growth of our wonderful staff.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Application Form:  Coming soon
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          <span style="text-decoration: underline;">
           ________________________________________________________________________
          </span>
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          <a href="https://retirees.ucsc.edu/scholarships/silver-slug-scholarship/index.html">
           Silver Slug Award Scholarship
          </a>
          <br/>
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
         The "Silver Slug Award” is a scholarship intended for current and retired staff and their dependents studying at UCSC who need financial assistance. The application period is now closed.  Recipients will be notified by the end of March 2019.
         <a href="https://retirees.ucsc.edu/scholarships/silver-slug-scholarship/index.html">
          <span style="text-decoration: underline;">
          </span>
         </a>
         <span style="text-decoration: underline;">
